text: Thomas Michael Simons (born 9 April 2004), better known as TommyInnit ( ), is an English YouTuber and Twitch streamer. ==Works== He makes "" Minecraft"" videos and livestreams. He works with other YouTubers and streamers in a roleplay group called the Dream SMP. , his seven YouTube channels have reached over million subscribers and over billion views. His main Twitch channel has reached over 7.2 million followers. This makes him the most-followed Minecraft channel on Twitch, and the 14th most-followed overall. == References == == Notes == == Other websites == * * Category:British YouTubers Category:2004 births Category:Living people
